cu.explanation_en: Setting drb_ciphering to an invalid enum value will cause security configuration parsing failure and prevent proper ciphering setup in the CU.

du.explanation_en: Setting modelname to an invalid enum value will cause RF simulator initialization failure and prevent proper radio frequency simulation in the DU.
du.explanation_zh: 將 modelname 設定為無效的枚舉值會導致 RF 模擬器初始化失敗，並阻止 DU 中的正確無線電頻率模擬。
